title: Calvin Klein Obsession For Men, Eau De Toilette Spray, 2.5 Ounce
description: Introduced in 1986. Fragrance notes: mandarin and spice, with low tones of musk, sandalwood and amber. Recommended use: daytime.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied
